<Layout title="Bonus & AWS (13th Month) Tax Treatment in Singapore | SalaryCalculator.sg" description="How bonuses, AWS (13th month salary), and variable pay are taxed and subject to CPF in Singapore. Covers Additional Wage ceiling, tax brackets, and planning strategies.">
